Name: gpsFix
Description: GPSfix Type, this value does not qualify a fix asvalid and within the limits. See note on flaggpsFixOk below.0x00 = no fix0x01 = dead reckoning only0x02 = 2D-fix0x03 = 3D-fix0x04 = GPS + dead reckoning combined0x05 = Time only fix0x06..0xff = reserved

Name: flags2
Description: further information about navigation output(see graphic below)

Name: ttff
Description: Time to first fix (millisecond time tag)
